@availabilityID = <availability_uuid>


### Get availability by professional ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/availabilities/professional/{{professionalID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Create availability (shift-based)
POST {{baseUrl}}/availabilities
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "professional_id": "{{professionalID}}",
  "day_of_week": ["MONDAY", "WEDNESDAY", "FRIDAY"],
  "shift": ["MORNING", "AFTERNOON"]
}


### Create availability (custom hours)
POST {{baseUrl}}/availabilities/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "professional_id": "{{professionalID}}",
  "day_of_week": ["TUESDAY", "THURSDAY"],
  "shift": ["CUSTOM"],
  "start_hour": "09:00",
  "end_hour": "18:00"
}


### Update availability
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/availabilities/{{availabilityID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "day_of_week": ["MONDAY", "TUESDAY", "WEDNESDAY"],
  "shift": ["MORNING"]
}


### Delete availability
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/availabilities/{{availabilityID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
